   "author_association" : "MEMBER",
   "body" : "This PR adds a new feature I found useful for testing (e.g., on Wayland) and debugging issues like #17153:\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ ./src/qt/bitcoin-qt -help-debug | grep -A 1 -e '-host'\r\n  -host\r\n       Print short info about the host system and exit\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ ./src/qt/bitcoin-qt -host\r\nHost Info\r\n  system: Linux Mint 19.3\r\n  arch:   x86_64-little_endian-lp64\r\n  screen: HDMI-1 1600x1200\r\n  ratio:  1.0\r\n  plugin: xcb (dynamic)\r\n```\r\n\r\nSimilar info could be added to the `debug.log` in followups.",
